description: Extract and transfer website design language with the repository's portable CLI or MCP tools
alwaysApply: true
---

For website style extraction, transfer, or reconstruction, read `SKILL.md`. Run `html2style doctor`, use the `full` viewport profile unless speed materially matters, and do not require a Cursor-specific browser integration. Default style work to `style-profile.json`, `STYLE.md`, and `style-board.html`, then run `html2style skill` so the final design-style Skill works in later sessions and includes an HTML preview. For complete replicas, read `references/high-fidelity-reconstruction.md`, validate asset URLs, and audit original versus replica evidence before declaring completion.
